long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get questions and answers from stackoverflow, when you search on google. The stackoverflow results will be displayed on the right side of the normal google search results. The stackoverflow results will only be shown if a coding word is included in the search query (for example one of these: "js", "javascript", "css", "python", "php", "string").
